賠錢收檔未"},{"pid":"4caeb64731406f6e5463d30bf5519b5d272cbd1e","tid":1002404,"uid":57787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cef456c4c0930aa5d335b8051f03a55174cda3aa","tid":1002404,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:25:20.000Z","msg":"重勁過大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:38:07.000Z","msg":"又未至於嘅，支那玩偷工減料始終玩咗幾十年，香港得廿年貨仔，仲有排追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be40268bda983b61e13bcb3853508bd216d2ec1e","tid":1002404,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"快啲開車啦<br />\n時間會話俾世人知個工程有無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81bf8c35f65cc2ea222783cdb7efa0fe6c55a34","tid":1002404,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"應該交由專業人仕去判斷<br />\n市民無需過份揣測!"},{"pid":"096fd54db92e5b457494283b021eda73b6e8a02e","tid":1002404,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9c52fdf840dc64a1d8d6e813db26e9408bba147","tid":1002404,"uid":152476,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"香港已經痴晒線<br />\n已經唔係講民主自由<br />\n基本專業操守都消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"９７前有半民主，全自由，有法治講規舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n９７後冇民主（得個橡皮圖章），冇自由（有紅線迫你愛蟈），冇法治（只有ＲＵＬＥ　ＢＹ　ＬＡＷ）冇規舉（黨治只講忠字舞）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598161345a19f4b5a67ab50bc139efe6bdc44a8c","tid":1002404,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d81bf8c35f65cc2ea222783cdb7efa0fe6c55a34","tid":1002404,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"應該交由專業人仕去判斷<br />\n市民無需過份揣測!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"今次到邊個話ok就ok?"},{"pid":"a002bfd6cd17e1d9acacee175d47a38f758d84a0","tid":1002404,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e026ee8f226c99ca384cf2c6bf7678629aeccfd7","tid":1002404,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:21:07.000Z","msg":"負責人冚家已退休移民。"},{"pid":"96d299fa9d03df2fa575101ed06246946b8c99f8","tid":1002404,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:25:35.000Z","msg":"佢最撚正係話冇證據證明唔安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家反智到唔係要證明安全，而係冇證據唔安全就得"},{"pid":"de70d01a9c56d2acdabf026b711aa1541b914ddd","tid":1002404,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"拆撚晒佢再起過啦<br />\n香港人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368918e4dc619777a33a82cd477dde462cb4c432","tid":1002404,"uid":221237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"無文件，調查無法繼續<br />\nclosed file"},{"pid":"cd280ba0cf9f57759c46a4ad30eb4374a84b9445","tid":1002404,"uid":4811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"首先炒咗陳煩先"}]}